data.description: Beautiful Split Foyer in West Jefferson with Newly Remodeled Kitchen! New Roof 2017. Excellent location with private setting but at the same time being close to everything. Large private yard, covered front porch and open deck on rear. This 3 bedroom, 3 bath home features open living area that is great for entertaining, crown molding, custom built bookshelves in living room and vaulted ceilings in the kitchen, dining and living room. Recent updates include new bathroom flooring 2009, new hardwood in the hall, living room, kitchen, dining and living rooms in 2010, new ceramic tile in the foyer and laundry rooms in 2011, new heat pump 2011. Finished area in basement has nice large den . Huge yard with plenty of room for outdoor activities. Child's playhouse has electricity.
